1
00:00:13,100 --> 00:00:15,600
Why are you here Hyeon Ho?

2
00:00:18,300 --> 00:00:20,300
You're here.

3
00:00:22,100 --> 00:00:26,500
President! These are the two new members I allowed to join.

4
00:00:27,800 --> 00:00:30,000
Please have a seat.

5
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:31,500
Okay.

6
00:00:44,400 --> 00:00:46,100
Well...

7
00:00:46,100 --> 00:00:49,500
Then let's begin the orientation.

8
00:00:49,500 --> 00:00:51,900
[Welcome]

9
00:00:57,500 --> 00:01:01,400
[Best Mistake 3]

10
00:01:01,400 --> 00:01:04,800
That's it for today's orientation.

11
00:01:04,800 --> 00:01:06,600
Please go home safely.

12
00:01:19,700 --> 00:01:21,400
I need to talk to you.

13
00:01:30,900 --> 00:01:32,200
Ye Seok—

14
00:01:45,500 --> 00:01:46,800
What's with you?!

15
00:01:46,800 --> 00:01:51,400
Following me is not enough so now you're joining the club?

16
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:52,600
Can't I?

17
00:01:52,600 --> 00:01:54,300
Do you really have to?

18
00:01:54,300 --> 00:01:58,800
Are you going to keep on following me and making me uncomfortable?

19
00:01:58,800 --> 00:02:00,700
Why are you uncomfortable?

20
00:02:00,700 --> 00:02:02,000
You said it's all over.

21
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:03,300
Well...

22
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:10,300
Okay.

23
00:02:10,300 --> 00:02:12,200
If you really want to join, go ahead.

24
00:02:12,200 --> 00:02:14,100
I'll leave.

25
00:02:14,100 --> 00:02:16,100
I really can't do it with you.

26
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:22,200
Why can't you do it with me?

27
00:02:24,200 --> 00:02:26,900
Can I understand that as lingering affection?

28
00:02:29,300 --> 00:02:31,200
No, it's not.

29
00:02:47,000 --> 00:02:48,200
Wait!

30
00:02:54,300 --> 00:02:56,900
I see you often.

31
00:02:56,900 --> 00:02:59,200
You keep coming to someone else's school too often, don't you?

32
00:02:59,200 --> 00:03:00,400
I came to the club.

33
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:01,800
The club?

34
00:03:01,800 --> 00:03:04,000
An intercollegiate club.

35
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:07,500
Why does an intercollegiate club keep meeting at our school?

36
00:03:07,500 --> 00:03:09,600
You!

37
00:03:09,600 --> 00:03:11,700
Just do only your club activities and leave, okay?

38
00:03:11,700 --> 00:03:15,000
Stop snooping in the classroom or the library like last time.

39
00:03:15,000 --> 00:03:16,400
Understand?

40
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:18,800
Assistant.

41
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:20,700
I'm a busy guy.

42
00:03:20,700 --> 00:03:23,400
I have no time to snoop around.

43
00:03:25,100 --> 00:03:27,400
Look at that attitude!

44
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:30,800
He's talking back to every word.

45
00:03:46,300 --> 00:03:48,400
Do you have something to say to me?

46
00:03:51,300 --> 00:03:52,800
You don't?

47
00:03:52,800 --> 00:03:54,200
Then I'm going.

48
00:03:54,200 --> 00:03:56,220
What are you up to?

49
00:03:57,400 --> 00:03:58,300
What?

50
00:03:58,300 --> 00:04:00,800
I don't know what you're thinking,

51
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:03,200
but don't mess with Ye Seok.

52
00:04:03,200 --> 00:04:04,900
After you left like that,

53
00:04:04,900 --> 00:04:07,680
he suffered like hell.

54
00:04:08,900 --> 00:04:11,900
Now he's breathing for life.

55
00:04:11,900 --> 00:04:14,000
Don't mess with him again.

56
00:04:18,900 --> 00:04:21,400
If you do that again,

57
00:04:23,500 --> 00:04:25,900
I won't stay still.

58
00:04:28,400 --> 00:04:29,700
Are you warning me?

59
00:04:29,700 --> 00:04:31,700
No, I'm begging you.

60
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:58,700
Have a sip.

61
00:04:58,700 --> 00:05:00,660
Thanks.

62
00:05:01,300 --> 00:05:02,300
So

63
00:05:02,300 --> 00:05:04,100
what will you do now?

64
00:05:04,100 --> 00:05:06,700
Will you be able to continue club activities?

65
00:05:06,700 --> 00:05:08,000
Just withdraw from it.

66
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:09,600
Withdraw?

67
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:15,100
No.

68
00:05:15,100 --> 00:05:16,000
What?

69
00:05:16,000 --> 00:05:19,800
If I withdraw, it means I have a lingering affection.

70
00:05:19,800 --> 00:05:22,500
I will show him that's not the case.

71
00:05:22,500 --> 00:05:24,800
I have to do it.

72
00:05:26,200 --> 00:05:29,200
You're not so easy, Yeon Du.

73
00:05:36,200 --> 00:05:38,100
We're having Seo Ju Ho's welcome party today!

74
00:05:38,100 --> 00:05:40,100
Please attend if you're free!

75
00:05:40,100 --> 00:05:42,200
Right! I heard Ju Ho is back.

76
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:44,300
- Did you meet him?
- Yes.

77
00:05:44,300 --> 00:05:45,800
A few days ago.

78
00:05:45,800 --> 00:05:47,800
Wow... So then...

79
00:05:47,800 --> 00:05:51,200
Is today your first day as a couple?

80
00:05:51,200 --> 00:05:52,000
Yes!

81
00:05:52,000 --> 00:05:54,800
- Congratulations!
- First day to have a crush!

82
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:56,300
What?

83
00:05:57,900 --> 00:06:00,000
I told Ju Ho

84
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:02,800
to have a crush on me.

85
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:04,200
Why?

86
00:06:04,200 --> 00:06:08,100
You were waiting for Ju Ho to come back.

87
00:06:08,100 --> 00:06:10,995
I've liked him first since high school,

88
00:06:10,995 --> 00:06:12,900
and I confessed first.

89
00:06:12,900 --> 00:06:14,800
Even after he went to study abroad,

90
00:06:14,800 --> 00:06:18,400
I was the only one to miss him so much.

91
00:06:19,300 --> 00:06:22,500
It seems I was the only one who was antsy.

92
00:06:22,500 --> 00:06:24,300
That's why

93
00:06:24,300 --> 00:06:27,400
I told him to feel how I felt.

94
00:06:28,300 --> 00:06:29,800
Seol,

95
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:31,200
are you all right?

96
00:06:31,200 --> 00:06:32,600
Do you think I am?

97
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:35,200
Of course, I'm not.

98
00:06:35,200 --> 00:06:36,900
I feel uncomfortable, too.

99
00:06:36,900 --> 00:06:38,600
And nervous.

100
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:40,300
At this rate,

101
00:06:40,300 --> 00:06:43,900
he might suddenly leave me again.

102
00:06:43,900 --> 00:06:46,600
Then why didn't you just accept him?

103
00:06:48,500 --> 00:06:51,100
It's not that easy.

104
00:06:52,400 --> 00:06:55,100
He might feel differently about me.

105
00:06:55,100 --> 00:06:57,800
Not as much as how I feel about him.

106
00:06:58,900 --> 00:07:01,900
So it's hard for me to start dating him.

107
00:07:01,900 --> 00:07:05,773
So you want to be assured of his love.

108
00:07:06,700 --> 00:07:10,200
Ask Ju Ho to reassure his love.

109
00:07:25,100 --> 00:07:26,700
Hey!

110
00:07:26,700 --> 00:07:29,300
Let's say they're like that.

111
00:07:29,300 --> 00:07:31,700
What's with them?

112
00:07:31,700 --> 00:07:34,500
I'm not sure, but...

113
00:07:34,500 --> 00:07:35,700
Seo Ju Ho

114
00:07:35,756 --> 00:07:37,044
asked Ryu Seol out and got dumped.

115
00:07:37,044 --> 00:07:39,917
- What?
- Shhh!

116
00:07:40,900 --> 00:07:43,200
Phew! Hold on.

117
00:07:43,200 --> 00:07:44,500
Hey!

118
00:07:44,500 --> 00:07:46,400
You knew about it.

119
00:07:46,400 --> 00:07:48,000
Then what is this combination?

120
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:50,700
Is this the best you could do?

121
00:07:50,700 --> 00:07:53,100
This is not what I intended.

122
00:07:53,100 --> 00:07:55,600
I just asked for people who would be free to come.

123
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:57,800
And that happened to be them.

124
00:07:57,800 --> 00:08:00,500
Then you should've canceled!

125
00:08:00,500 --> 00:08:03,300
Hey! How can I cancel when I asked them to come?

126
00:08:03,300 --> 00:08:06,000
Still, you should have.

127
00:08:08,900 --> 00:08:10,000
Oh?

128
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:12,100
Yeon Du.

129
00:08:12,100 --> 00:08:14,000
Senior Dae Yeong.

130
00:08:35,000 --> 00:08:38,100
What brings you here, Senior?

131
00:08:38,100 --> 00:08:41,500
Dae Yeong asked for a drink.

132
00:08:41,500 --> 00:08:44,870
Running into you like this is a bit amazing.

133
00:08:54,100 --> 00:08:56,200
I didn't know you were here, Seol.

134
00:08:56,200 --> 00:08:59,227
Oh... yes.

135
00:09:12,562 --> 00:09:14,712
Hmm...

136
00:09:14,712 --> 00:09:16,000
So...

137
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:19,300
You two are Squirtle's... No.

138
00:09:19,300 --> 00:09:23,400
Yeon Du's seniors at school and at the club.

139
00:09:23,400 --> 00:09:25,700
But in that club,

140
00:09:25,700 --> 00:09:27,500
Hyeon Ho is also there?

141
00:09:27,500 --> 00:09:31,200
That's right. How many times do I have to tell you?

142
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:32,700
And you two

143
00:09:32,700 --> 00:09:35,274
somehow got to know each other?

144
00:09:35,274 --> 00:09:37,400
What do you mean somehow?

145
00:09:37,400 --> 00:09:41,200
This is all fate and destiny.

146
00:09:42,200 --> 00:09:43,600
What's he saying?

147
00:09:43,600 --> 00:09:44,900
Don't mind him.

148
00:09:44,900 --> 00:09:48,700
He's always talking about destiny.

149
00:09:48,700 --> 00:09:50,400
Oh...

150
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:53,900
Destiny... Destiny...

151
00:09:56,500 --> 00:09:58,400
No way!

152
00:10:00,100 --> 00:10:02,500
Do you believe in destiny?

153
00:10:02,500 --> 00:10:04,100
Well...

154
00:10:04,700 --> 00:10:06,800
You know something!

155
00:10:06,800 --> 00:10:08,733
I also believe in destiny!

156
00:10:08,733 --> 00:10:10,300
When I was in high school,

157
00:10:10,300 --> 00:10:12,000
I dreamed about meeting Wang Ying Ling.

158
00:10:12,000 --> 00:10:13,800
And the very following semester!

159
00:10:13,800 --> 00:10:15,200
I met Wang Ying Ling.

160
00:10:15,200 --> 00:10:18,400
Is this destiny or what?

161
00:10:18,400 --> 00:10:20,452
Oh...

162
00:10:20,452 --> 00:10:21,992
Just ignore him.

163
00:10:22,017 --> 00:10:25,708
He likes to talk gibberish. Romance, in a good way—

164
00:10:25,708 --> 00:10:27,600
Destiny!

165
00:10:31,400 --> 00:10:33,400
It's destiny.

166
00:10:34,400 --> 00:10:36,000
Destined by Heaven.

167
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:38,000
Destiny.

168
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:40,000
I knew it!

169
00:10:40,000 --> 00:10:42,200
I knew you'd understand me.

170
00:10:42,200 --> 00:10:44,300
No. Don't call me, "You."

171
00:10:44,300 --> 00:10:48,300
Call me, "Hyung." Little Bro Ji Seong.

172
00:10:48,300 --> 00:10:50,400
Yes, Hyung!

173
00:10:51,109 --> 00:10:53,040
Um... Well, okay!

174
00:10:53,040 --> 00:10:56,300
Since we're all destined to be here, let's say cheers.

175
00:10:56,300 --> 00:10:57,654
Oh, good timing.

176
00:10:57,654 --> 00:11:00,300
- Good! Good!
- Hold on!

177
00:11:00,300 --> 00:11:03,200
It's no fun to just drink.

178
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:05,200
With the person next to you,

179
00:11:05,200 --> 00:11:07,000
how about a love shot?

180
00:11:07,000 --> 00:11:08,900
What?

181
00:11:08,900 --> 00:11:10,700
What do you mean a love shot?

182
00:11:10,700 --> 00:11:11,900
Let's just say cheers together.

183
00:11:11,900 --> 00:11:13,700
What's the matter?

184
00:11:13,700 --> 00:11:15,200
If it's with you, Hyung,

185
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:16,900
I can do a love shot.

186
00:11:16,900 --> 00:11:19,300
But a love shot is too much.

187
00:11:19,300 --> 00:11:24,560
Love shot! Love shot! Love shot!

188
00:11:24,560 --> 00:11:30,020
Love shot! Love shot! Love shot!

189
00:11:37,100 --> 00:11:39,100
Are you going to spill on my shirt again?

190
00:11:39,100 --> 00:11:41,500
I'll drink instead.

191
00:11:45,721 --> 00:11:47,297
Oh...

192
00:11:49,900 --> 00:11:51,100
What?

193
00:11:51,100 --> 00:11:53,000
What's that?

194
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:55,200
Hyeon Ho and Hyung Ye Seok

195
00:11:55,200 --> 00:11:58,300
are going to do a love shot together?

196
00:11:58,300 --> 00:12:00,200
Hyung, my butt.

197
00:12:00,200 --> 00:12:03,100
And I'm not doing a love shot.

198
00:12:10,100 --> 00:12:12,900
What's this? It's no fun.

199
00:12:12,900 --> 00:12:14,900
Let's just drink altogether.

200
00:12:14,900 --> 00:12:16,500
Everyone, raise your glasses with me.

201
00:12:16,500 --> 00:12:19,505
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

202
00:12:19,505 --> 00:12:22,791
- Nice to meet you.
- Nice to see you.

203
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:29,500
How is the food, Seol? Is it good to you?

204
00:12:29,500 --> 00:12:32,000
- It's not good.
- Oh, it's good. It's okay.

205
00:12:54,700 --> 00:12:55,800
Seol.

206
00:12:55,800 --> 00:12:57,600
Drinking coffee is good,

207
00:12:57,600 --> 00:12:59,800
but drink this first.

208
00:12:59,800 --> 00:13:01,700
Thanks.

209
00:13:10,800 --> 00:13:13,200
- Seol.
- Yes?

210
00:13:14,400 --> 00:13:16,600
What you said before...

211
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:19,200
"Having a crush on you."

212
00:13:19,200 --> 00:13:20,700
Yes.

213
00:13:20,700 --> 00:13:22,500
Until when

214
00:13:22,500 --> 00:13:25,400
should I have it?

215
00:13:32,600 --> 00:13:33,800
Why are you asking?

216
00:13:33,800 --> 00:13:35,400
Can't you do it?

217
00:13:35,400 --> 00:13:36,800
No!

218
00:13:36,800 --> 00:13:39,700
No, that's not what I meant.

219
00:13:39,700 --> 00:13:41,200
It's just that...

220
00:13:41,200 --> 00:13:44,300
While I'm having a crush on you,

221
00:13:44,300 --> 00:13:47,300
You might come to like someone else.

222
00:13:49,100 --> 00:13:51,300
By any chance, it could happen.

223
00:13:51,300 --> 00:13:53,600
- You did, too.
- What?

224
00:13:53,600 --> 00:13:55,700
When I had a crush on you,

225
00:13:55,700 --> 00:13:58,100
you used to like Kim Yeon Du.

226
00:13:58,100 --> 00:13:59,800
Why can't I do the same?

227
00:13:59,800 --> 00:14:01,300
Well, that...

228
00:14:01,300 --> 00:14:03,324
I really didn't know that you liked me.

229
00:14:03,324 --> 00:14:04,900
Don't worry.

230
00:14:04,900 --> 00:14:07,300
I won't be the same.

231
00:14:10,300 --> 00:14:13,800
I'm not together or anything with that guy.

232
00:14:14,800 --> 00:14:16,200
Is that so?

233
00:14:28,100 --> 00:14:30,100
Finally!

234
00:14:30,100 --> 00:14:32,600
It is our first photography outing.

235
00:14:32,600 --> 00:14:36,200
You will be in groups of two, a female and a male, and take photos.

236
00:14:36,200 --> 00:14:40,900
We'll select teams fair and square by

237
00:14:40,900 --> 00:14:43,365
ghost leg.

238
00:14:46,400 --> 00:14:48,000
Friend.

239
00:14:48,000 --> 00:14:49,600
If it's for you,

240
00:14:49,600 --> 00:14:53,100
I'm willing to sell myself out.

241
00:14:55,267 --> 00:15:00,200
Then shall we start with Member Do Ye Seok?

242
00:15:07,413 --> 00:15:10,600
Do Ye Seok, you're in the same team as Kim Yeon Du.

243
00:15:10,600 --> 00:15:15,100
Congratu— No, I mean, have a good photo session!

244
00:15:20,000 --> 00:15:23,400
Member Ji Hyeon Ho is in the same team as Member Jin Se Hui.

245
00:15:23,400 --> 00:15:26,000
Good luck, you two.

246
00:15:27,800 --> 00:15:30,600
Then shall we go?

247
00:15:39,500 --> 00:15:41,700
Is it okay?

248
00:15:41,700 --> 00:15:43,700
Yes, very.

249
00:15:43,700 --> 00:15:46,150
I'll continue.

250
00:15:46,950 --> 00:15:49,000
♫ 0 percent in one day ♫

251
00:15:49,000 --> 00:15:53,000
The angle is...

252
00:15:53,000 --> 00:15:54,750
♫ this much ♫

253
00:15:54,750 --> 00:15:56,400
♫ I'm going forward to you ♫

254
00:15:56,400 --> 00:15:58,000
Oh, that's good.

255
00:15:58,000 --> 00:15:59,990
Hold on.

256
00:15:59,990 --> 00:16:03,130
♫ You know I'm getting closer ♫

257
00:16:03,130 --> 00:16:05,500
♫ Run faster toward me ♫

258
00:16:05,500 --> 00:16:09,700
One, two...

259
00:16:09,700 --> 00:16:11,600
Put your hands like this.

260
00:16:11,600 --> 00:16:14,000
Like this.

261
00:16:14,000 --> 00:16:15,600
And your face, like this.

262
00:16:15,600 --> 00:16:18,700
Good.

263
00:16:18,700 --> 00:16:20,600
It's good!

264
00:16:20,600 --> 00:16:23,200
One, two, three!

265
00:16:23,200 --> 00:16:24,500
Oh, it's good.

266
00:16:24,500 --> 00:16:27,200
One, two, three.

267
00:16:27,200 --> 00:16:29,400
It looks so good.

268
00:16:29,400 --> 00:16:30,600
Tada!

269
00:16:30,600 --> 00:16:32,900
How is it? Didn't it come out well?

270
00:16:32,900 --> 00:16:34,200
Yes.

271
00:16:34,200 --> 00:16:36,600
Look, it looks really good.

272
00:16:36,600 --> 00:16:40,270
Are they dating or what?

273
00:16:40,270 --> 00:16:41,700
Senior, your photo came out very good.

274
00:16:41,700 --> 00:16:43,500
I know...

275
00:16:44,200 --> 00:16:46,700
Those two...

276
00:16:46,700 --> 00:16:49,500
They're not just a senior and a junior.

277
00:16:53,300 --> 00:16:56,100
They look like just a senior and a junior.

278
00:17:00,200 --> 00:17:02,400
I don't think so.

279
00:17:03,500 --> 00:17:07,200
Otherwise, Do Ye Seok wouldn't smile like that.

280
00:17:12,600 --> 00:17:13,800
Yeon Du!

281
00:17:13,800 --> 00:17:15,500
Oh, hi.

282
00:17:15,500 --> 00:17:19,400
By any chance, is Ji Hyeon Ho your ex?

283
00:17:22,000 --> 00:17:24,100
How did you know?

284
00:17:24,100 --> 00:17:25,303
How could I not?

285
00:17:25,303 --> 00:17:28,200
You two have the same vibe.

286
00:17:28,200 --> 00:17:30,800
Why did you two break up?

287
00:17:38,200 --> 00:17:39,900
Sorry, I was too impolite.

288
00:17:39,900 --> 00:17:42,700
No, it's okay.

289
00:17:44,200 --> 00:17:46,000
But...

290
00:17:46,000 --> 00:17:47,800
Are you okay?

291
00:17:47,800 --> 00:17:49,200
With Senior Ye Seok?

292
00:17:49,200 --> 00:17:51,500
Yes, of course.

293
00:17:51,500 --> 00:17:53,700
I got better in no time.

294
00:17:53,700 --> 00:17:55,300
That's a relief.

295
00:17:55,300 --> 00:17:57,300
Ye Seok is a really good guy.

296
00:17:57,300 --> 00:18:00,800
You'll see, Yeon Du.

297
00:18:03,200 --> 00:18:05,900
You might even fall in love.

298
00:18:05,900 --> 00:18:08,100
Or are you already in love?

299
00:18:08,100 --> 00:18:09,700
What are you saying?

300
00:18:09,700 --> 00:18:13,100
We're not like that.

301
00:18:13,100 --> 00:18:14,800
Is that so?

302
00:18:14,800 --> 00:18:19,100
I thought you two looked very close.

303
00:18:19,100 --> 00:18:22,500
We were recently in a group project, that's all.

304
00:18:22,500 --> 00:18:25,200
A group project?

305
00:18:26,300 --> 00:18:28,000
Together?

306
00:18:28,000 --> 00:18:31,551
Yes, we have a basic required class together.

307
00:18:32,800 --> 00:18:34,200
Oh...

308
00:18:34,200 --> 00:18:36,100
I see.

309
00:18:42,168 --> 00:18:43,647
What?

310
00:18:44,900 --> 00:18:45,900
Hey!

311
00:18:45,900 --> 00:18:47,200
How is the date coming?

312
00:18:47,200 --> 00:18:48,800
What date...

313
00:18:48,800 --> 00:18:51,300
You know.

314
00:18:51,300 --> 00:18:52,900
With Yeon Du, hmm?

315
00:18:52,900 --> 00:18:55,800
How is it going?

316
00:18:55,800 --> 00:18:57,900
It's just a club activity.

317
00:18:57,900 --> 00:18:59,600
That's a bummer if you say just like that.

318
00:18:59,600 --> 00:19:02,400
You don't know what I did for you.

319
00:19:02,400 --> 00:19:04,700
What did you do?

320
00:19:10,300 --> 00:19:11,600
It doesn't matter.

321
00:19:11,600 --> 00:19:12,900
So...

322
00:19:12,900 --> 00:19:14,900
How was the club activity?

323
00:19:14,900 --> 00:19:17,200
Let me see your photos.

324
00:19:17,200 --> 00:19:19,400
Give them to me!

325
00:19:21,400 --> 00:19:22,400
Hey!

326
00:19:22,400 --> 00:19:25,800
They're all photos of Yeon Du!

327
00:19:25,800 --> 00:19:28,400
Even if you like her so much...

328
00:19:29,980 --> 00:19:31,580
"Like."

329
00:19:32,400 --> 00:19:34,100
Well... Um...

330
00:19:34,100 --> 00:19:36,600
You said to take portraits,

331
00:19:36,600 --> 00:19:38,300
so I took portraits.

332
00:19:38,300 --> 00:19:39,200
Hey.

333
00:19:39,200 --> 00:19:41,600
Still, this is too obvious.

334
00:19:41,600 --> 00:19:45,400
There should be other photos as well.

335
00:19:47,500 --> 00:19:50,900
In that sense, take a photo of me.

336
00:19:53,000 --> 00:19:54,200
Come here.

337
00:19:54,200 --> 00:19:56,500
How is this?

338
00:19:57,300 --> 00:19:58,300
What do you think?

339
00:19:58,300 --> 00:20:00,300
The weather is nice.

340
00:20:00,300 --> 00:20:02,200
It's going to look good.

341
00:20:02,200 --> 00:20:04,400
- Darn.
- Hurry!

342
00:20:05,547 --> 00:20:06,913
Hey! Where are you going?

343
00:20:06,913 --> 00:20:09,300
- Don't follow me.
- Just one photo?

344
00:20:09,300 --> 00:20:11,000
You all did a good job!

345
00:20:11,000 --> 00:20:13,400
See you next week!

346
00:20:25,900 --> 00:20:28,900
Isn't the club activity over?

347
00:20:28,900 --> 00:20:30,600
I heard you two went out.

348
00:20:30,600 --> 00:20:32,600
With Kim Yeon Du.

349
00:20:35,400 --> 00:20:36,900
How could I know?

350
00:20:36,900 --> 00:20:39,400
Yeon Du told me.

351
00:20:41,100 --> 00:20:43,500
You seem to have broken up recently.

352
00:20:47,100 --> 00:20:49,000
You...

353
00:20:49,000 --> 00:20:51,800
still like her, don't you?

354
00:20:53,700 --> 00:20:55,600
No?

355
00:20:56,800 --> 00:20:59,700
Why should I answer to you?

356
00:20:59,700 --> 00:21:02,197
Because I like Do Ye Seok.

357
00:21:04,200 --> 00:21:06,800
Speaking of which...

358
00:21:06,800 --> 00:21:09,000
Do you want to join forces?

359
00:21:21,312 --> 00:21:24,653
[Best Mistake 3]

360
00:21:24,701 --> 00:21:27,713
When four 20 year olds visit, you get a combo fries for free?

361
00:21:27,800 --> 00:21:31,200
When four 20 year olds visit, you get all this for free!

362
00:21:37,230 --> 00:21:43,950
♫ The two of us that seems 100 percent close and perfect ♫

363
00:21:45,150 --> 00:21:48,100
Do Ye Seok who bumps into her dozen times a day

364
00:21:48,100 --> 00:21:50,300
has a significant advantage?

365
00:21:50,300 --> 00:21:52,200
I like you, Seol.

366
00:21:52,200 --> 00:21:54,100
Do you want to bet who wins?

367
00:21:54,100 --> 00:21:55,700
Don't you hate Kim Yeon Du?

368
00:21:55,700 --> 00:21:57,900
That's how she is.

369
00:21:57,900 --> 00:22:01,870
Yes, that's how she is.

370
00:22:01,870 --> 00:22:08,500
♫ Run faster toward me ♫

371
00:22:08,500 --> 00:22:12,126
[Best Mistake 3]
